  "title": "Geotechnical Engineer (New Viaduct)/5day/Upto $7.5K+VB",
  "description": "<p><strong>• Participating in new LTA project [Viaduct and Station]</strong><br /><strong>• Having experience in airport civil work or LTA project [Viaduct and Station] is mandatory.</strong><br /><strong>• 2 x openings/ Permanent role/ 5 workdays/ West area </strong><br /><strong>• MNCs & leading A1 main contractor</strong></p><p><br /><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Geotechnical Coordination:</strong> Coordinate all geotechnical works for construction projects. </p></li><li><p><strong>Site Issue Resolution:</strong> Address and resolve site issues promptly, including RFIs, CO substantiations, and material costing. </p></li><li><p><strong>Design Management:</strong> Coordinate with consultants and liaise with authorities for project design updates and submissions. Liaise and coordinate with other stakeholders and consultants on the design and technical issues relating to temporary works.</p></li><li><p><strong>Liaison with Stakeholders:</strong> Coordinate with internal and external parties, including authorities, to resolve design discrepancies and construction issues. Attend meetings with clients, subcontractors, consultants, and other relevant stakeholders.</p></li><li><p><strong>Issue Resolution:</strong> Manage and resolve production, quality, design, engineering, and scheduling issues.</p></li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Degree in Civil Engineering and/or relevant field</p></li><li><p>Experience in LTA project [Viaduct and Station] is mandatory.</p></li></ul><p><br /><strong>To apply, please include the following details inside your resume:</strong><br />• Reasons for leaving each past & current employment<br />• Salary drawn for each past & current employment<br />• Expected Salary<br />• Earliest availability date<br /><strong>How to apply</strong><br />Interested candidates who wish to apply for the position, you may send in your updated resume to <a href=\"mailto:search84@searchindex.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">search84@searchindex.com.sg</a><br /><strong>We regret that only short-listed candidates will be contacted shortly.</strong><br /><strong>Lionel Cheow</strong></p><p><strong>EA License | 14C7092</strong><br /><strong>EA Registration Number | R1105005</strong></p>",
